These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-1::.
3 different pets are kept: mouse, bird, hedgehog
There are 3 different nationalities: polish, spanish, canadian
1. the owner of the mouse is in an even position##4
2. the polish is on the left or right of the canadian##3
3. the polish is the owner of the bird##1
4. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far left##1
5. the spanish is the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Pet   | hedgehog | mouse | bird |
| Nationality    | spanish    | canadian | polish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-2::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: techno, reggae, country
There are 3 different favourite beverages: tea, almond-milk, cola
1. the fan of techno is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is in an even position##4
3. the person drinking cola is on the left of the fan of country##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk is the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Music-Genre       | reggae | country | techno |
| Beverage   | cola    | almond-milk     | tea        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-3::.
3 different games are played: billiard, scrabble, monopoly
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, coffee, iced-tea
1. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
2. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
3. the person playing scrabble is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3    |
| Game         | monopoly     | scrabble | billiard |
| Beverage   | coffee | milk     | iced-tea  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-4::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, october, september
The people have 3 different jobs:  lawyer, firefighter, dancer
1. the person who's birthday is in october is the firefighter##1
2. the person who's birthday is in july is the dancer##1
3. the person who's birthday is in october is in an even position##4
4. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |
| Birthday   | september | october  | july  |
| Job         | lawyer  | firefighter | dancer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-5::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, scooter, boat
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: documentary, horror, scientific
1. the person driving the boat is between the person driving the airplane and the person watching documentary movies##2
2. the person driving the scooter is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Transport         | airplane   | boat | scooter    |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | scientific     | documentary |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-6::.
There 3 different types of food: tomato, raspberry, banana
There are 3 different favourite colors: blood-red, coral, black
1. the person eating tomato is the person who likes coral##1
2. the person who likes black is the person eating raspberry##1
3. the person eating raspberry is in an odd position##4
4. the person eating banana is on the right of the person who likes black##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Food   | raspberry | banana | tomato   |
| Color   | black     | blood-red    | coral |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-7::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: collecting, singing, photography
There are 3 different nationalities: indonesian, german, mexican
1. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is between the mexican and the person who's hobby is photography##2
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
4. the indonesian is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |   3    |
| Hobby   | photography | collecting | singing |
| Nationality           | german         | indonesian         | mexican |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-8::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, game, oliveros
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, july, december
1. the person who's birthday is in january is between the person who's birthday is in july and the pall-mall-smoker##2
2. the person who's birthday is in december is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |     3     |
| Cigar   | game | oliveros | pall-mall |
| Birthday    | july    | january | december     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-9::.
There 3 different types of food: cucumber, banana, avocado
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, bike, jet-ski
1. the person driving the jet-ski is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1
3. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person eating banana##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the person driving the bike##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Food   | avocado   | banana  | cucumber  |
| Transport         | jet-ski | bike | helicopter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-10::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, documentary, spy
City: hamburg, prague, marseilles
1. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
2. the person traveling to marseilles is in an even position##4
3. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person watching action movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | action    | spy      | documentary |
| City       | prague | marseilles | hamburg   |

