.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-11::.
There are 3 different nationalities: italian, malaysian, brazilian
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, coffee
1. the brazilian is on the right of the malaysian##1
2. the person drinking 7up is the italian##1
3. the person drinking coffee is the brazilian##1
4. the brazilian is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |     3      |
| Nationality         | malaysian | brazilian | italian |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | coffee   | 7up |

