2. the person drinking cola is the art-deco house##1
3. the craftsman house is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
4. the art-deco house is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |
| Beverage   | 7up | milk | cola |
| House     | craftsman     | futuristic   | art-deco        |

