.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-14::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: gospel, r&b, house
The people use 3 different means of transport: jet-ski, car, quad-bike
1. the fan of house is between the fan of r&b and the person driving the car##2
2. the fan of r&b is in an odd position##4
3. the person driving the car is on the far left or far right##3
4. the fan of house is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | r&b | house | gospel |
| Transport     | jet-ski    | quad-bike  | car   |

