.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-15::.
3 different pets are kept: dog, lizard, chinchilla
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, october, december
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3
4. the owner of the chinchilla is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |
| Pet   | dog  | chinchilla     | lizard |
| Birthday   | october | august | december    |

