.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-17::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: satire, adventure, scientific
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, metal, classical
1. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
2. the fan of funk is on the right of the fan of classical##1
3. the fan of funk is in an odd position##4
4. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the fan of classical##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | scientific | adventure    |
| Music-Genre           | metal     | classical  | funk |

