.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-18::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: soccer, parkour, badminton
3 different games are played: backgammon, domino, monopoly
1. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
2. the person who's sport is soccer is in the middle##1
3. the person who's sport is badminton is the person playing domino##1
4. the person playing backgammon is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |
| Sport         | badminton | soccer   | parkour |
| Game   | domino   | backgammon | monopoly      |

