.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-19::.
House: futuristic, townhouse, colonial
There 3 different types of food: nectarine, cranberry, asparagus
1. the person eating asparagus is on the left or right of the futuristic house##3
2. the futuristic house is in an odd position##4
3. the colonial house is on the right of the townhouse house##1
4. the townhouse house is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |    3     |
| House      | futuristic | townhouse | colonial |
| Food   | cranberry   | asparagus          | nectarine |

