.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-20::.
There are 3 different nationalities: italian, colombian, spanish
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, daffodil, bellflower
1. the person who growsbellflower is in an odd position##4
2. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the spanish##1
3. the spanish is in an even position##4
4. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the colombian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3      |
| Nationality     | colombian  | spanish   | italian |
| Flower   | bellflower | daffodil | amaryllis       |

 